            <title>[GROOVY-4235] Closure returned from static method cannot access class properties through &quot;this&quot;</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-4235</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Given this code:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;class Foo {&lt;br/&gt;
    static prop = &quot;sadfs&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
    static foo() {&lt;br/&gt;
        return &lt;/p&gt;
{ -&amp;gt; println this.prop }
&lt;p&gt;    }&lt;br/&gt;
}&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Foo.foo().call()&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;A ClassCastException will be thrown even though printing out &quot;this&quot; inside of the closure prints out &quot;class Foo&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
